snippet.title: Ninja Pizza Girl - Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Combining mouth-watering game design, a tasty Kickstarter success and months of baking in the Early Access oven, Disparity Games are proud to show the Steam release trailer for Ninja Pizza Girl
